<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=96966678719488></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96966678719488><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=2&mid=96966678719488>Starting a dark elf rogue.</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=2&mid=96966678719488#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=1735><span id= >Elzoth</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Sep 22nd 7:53 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>1. First Thing, give your note to the leader of the ebon mask guild. Don the tunic you receive.<br>2. Equip the beginner's knife. (If you can twink yourself a scimitar or another low delay 1hs this works even better).<br>3. Go to the guild trainer and raise 1 point in piercing, 1 point in sneak, 1 point in one hand slash, 1 in throwing, and one in anything else you like.<br>4. Talk to all the guildmasters until you find the one who wants you to complete a quest. The quest he gives you requires that you fill a bag with three snake skins and three snake fangs. Take the free bag he gives you.<br>5. Now exit town and begin killing rampantly. At level 1 thru 3, NEVER rest, always kill yourself, and come back, you will have full life. When you have to rest or want to practice hide and sneak a bit, just hotbox them and do it while you're sitting. I recommend using the one hand slashers like a scimitar more than piercing at first, because the piercers are just too weak in comparison, until you get a bit higher.<br>6. Make sure to focus on killing WHITES almost exclusively. I have written an exp calculator and know that fighting whites only, not only raises combat skills faster, but gets vast more experience than blues will.<br>7. Also, make exceptions to kill every moss snake you can. Stack up as many skins and fangs as you can for the bag quest; and keep the eggs because they count as a food item. When you can, fill up the bag with three skins and three fangs (UNSTACKED), and return to the man who gave you the bag. You will get HUGE exp from doing this before 5th level, like around a third to half a bubble. And if you have many fangs and skins, you can simply get a new bag and fill it, and turn it in again for more exp!! This will also get you a dark shield of ebon as well.<br><br>This should get you to fifth level FAST, as a dark elf rogue. Have fun!<br><br>Elzoth.<br>&nbsp;<br>Elzoth, Dead Champion</td></tr>
