, i traded for the pants, NICE deal for me. heh). an some other nice item i won. dont know the name off hand. <br><br>so as for all you who say rogues cant tank, you ARE wrong, you jus havent gotten in the right group )<br><br>hope this helps all you mid high 20s rogues in the future for a great exp spot an group opportunites.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
