	   <tr><td colspan=2>got to a hotkey group,thene pick up the weapons inventory icon(by holding left mouse button on the inventory slot the weapon is in)thene place it in a hot key slot,do the same on your primary weapons icon,whene you are about to backstab,hit shift 2 (or whatever hotkey group your using)thene switch the higher dmg piercer with the one in your hand,backstab,and switch back.<br><br>I do this with slashing and piercing,but i use slashing untill backstab is ready (i use it as a frontal attack soloing)switch to the piercer,backstab in front and switch back (im only lvl 12 right now,hoping for 13 soon hehe!).<br><br>Backstab will NOT go up using it as a second attack,but i can deal about 26 dmg in one round using this (not bad for a rogue with a dragoon dirk at lvl 12)and since the dirk is very fast,i deal more dmg thene warriors (non-twinked) while soloing.<br><br>Have a good night,i hope this info helped =)<br> <br>Arrtemis<br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
