	   <tr><td colspan=2>On a related note.  You don't actually have to enter freeport to get to poison related things.  in West freeport, there is a wall you can walk through (in a corner to the left of the gates, looking inward).  This leads to the tunnel system under freeport.<br><br>In this tunnel system, is a dark elf.  His name is Toxdil.  He loves you.  He sells poison stuff (vials, suspensions, etc).  So, disregard the freeport guards, head into the tunnels, and just buy all the poison stuff you could ever want or need.<br><br>There is also a nice lad in Dagnor's Cauldron that sells poison stuff.  Not sure what his stance toward DE's is tho.  He seems to like my halfling.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
